==English==

===Noun===
'''[[mad]] [[money]]'''
*An emergency stash of money kept to insulate one from [[dependency]].  Mad money might be kept by an [[employee]] to allow the freedom to walk away from a [[job]] if it goes badly, or by a dependent [[spouse]], or in [[cash]] form by someone who doesn't fully trust [[bank]]s or who has reason to fear a [[lien]].

====Synonyms====
*[[fuck-you money]]